---
<BaseLayout
  title="Discover Alaska ‚Äî Travel Guides by Scott"
  description="Your immersive guide to Alaska ‚Äî glaciers, wildlife, northern lights, cuisine, and honest recommendations from real travel experience."
>
  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO ‚Äî 100vh cinematic with video background
       ============================================================ -->
